001522  1               ; hide_all_inv_sprites — set z-depth=0 for all 55 invader sprites
001522  1               ;   Uses VERA stride=8 to write only byte 6 (z-depth) of each block.
001522  1               ;   First invader sprite byte 6: $1FC00 + 11*8 + 6 = $1FC5E
001522  1               ;******************************************************************
001522  1               hide_all_inv_sprites:
